content: EU delegates announce additional commitment to phase out coal power by 2030, exceeding previous targets set in the agreement.
China confirms participation in new international carbon trading system, marking significant shift in environmental policy.
Youth climate activists gather outside summit venue, demanding stronger enforcement mechanisms for emission targets.
Phoenix Eagles' victory parade scheduled for tomorrow at 2 PM, expected to draw over 100,000 fans to downtown area.
Championship MVP Jake Morrison announces $1 million donation to youth sports programs in Phoenix.
